ink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Dez 27, 2022</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104fbn1665702616587.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/fbn1665702616587.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/fbn1665702616587.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"fbn1665702616587\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Determines the background color of panels.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"fbn1665702616587__topic_d146789e1_d146790e1_d146791e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fbn1665702616587__p_d146792e1_d146793e1_d146794e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">PanelColor</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Color</var></p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"fbn1665702616587__section_b55_4q1_zvb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d970914e64\">Arguments</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Color</var>— Windows color name or Web color name.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"fbn1665702616587__table_w3432ab1b5b3b5_w3433ab1b5b3_w3434ab1b5_w3435ab1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Default value</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">If no color is defined, uses the Windows system color.\n              </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">File section</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"yzj1665702614359.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yzj1665702614359.html\" title=\"The [upi] section of the initialization file determines the appearance or behavior of many Universal Presentation Interface (UPI) objects under Microsoft Windows.\">[upi]</a></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"fbn1665702616587__section_ucn_rq1_zvb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d970914e112\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">PanelColor</span> setting corresponds to the setting <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Toolbar and\n          Panel Color</span> in the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Toolbar</span> tab of the Uniface\n          <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Setup</span> dialog box. By default, it is set to <code class=\"ph codeph\">System\n          Default</code>.</p>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"fbn1665702616587__note_zg3_sq1_zvb\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> This property is not applied to a pop-up panel, which\n        is a panel that is displayed as a menu.</div>\n</section>\n<div class=\"example\" id=\"fbn1665702616587__example_uvq_sq1_zvb\">\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"fbn1665702616587__pre_vvq_sq1_zvb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">[upi]\npanelcolor=lightsteelblue1</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rcm1665702587635.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Standard Colors</a><p>Uniface supports standard color definitions including system colors as defined by the operating system, Web colors defined by the W3C, and RGB (red-green-blue) colors expressed in hex or decimal numbers. Any of these color definitions can be used when defining the value of foreground and background colors of components, widgets, panels, and toolbars.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yqt1665703084374.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Panels</a></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527430\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527430\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "PanelColor Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Dez 27, 2022 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Determines the background color of panels. PanelColor = Color Arguments Color — Windows color name or Web color name. Default value If no color is defined, uses the Windows system color. File section [upi] Description The PanelColor setting corresponds to the setting Toolbar and Panel Color in the Toolbar tab of the Uniface Setup dialog box. By default, it is set to System Default . Note: This property is not applied to a pop-up panel, which is a panel that is displayed as a menu. [upi] panelcolor=lightsteelblue1 Copy Related Links Standard Colors Uniface supports standard color definitions including system colors as defined by the operating system, Web colors defined by the W3C, and RGB (red-green-blue) colors expressed in hex or decimal numbers. Any of these color definitions can be used when defining the value of foreground and background colors of components, widgets, panels, and toolbars. Panels Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}